  <CaptionedBlock heading="Aftercare That's Already in the Price" imageAlt="Puppy aftercare included in the price: apricot Cavapoo resting on a caregiver's lap during a gentle ear check at home" imageSrc={aftercareLap} imagePosition="right" variant="card">
    <p>Support does not end when the delivery van leaves. If your puppy falls sick within the first 5 days of going home, bring them back to the shop and we will nurse them ourselves.</p>
    <p>Beyond that window, our customer service stays free: WhatsApp us any care question, any time. Most of them we will already have answered during the starter-kit walkthrough in your home, and the ones we haven't get a real reply from the people who matched you with your puppy.</p>
    <p>The free first lesson is with an <a href="https://avs.nparks.gov.sg/outreach/resources/acdt-dog-trainers/" class="underline underline-offset-2 text-[var(--color-accent-hover)]">AVS-Accredited Certified Dog Trainer</a>, best booked in your puppy's first week home.</p>
